<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/1fcfbf548a.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </head>
  <body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
      <div class="container-fluid">
          <a class="navbar-brand" href='#'><%= title %> Application</a>
          <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
              <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
              <ul class="navbar-nav">
                  <li class="nav-item">
                      <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
                  </li>
                  <li class="nav-item">
                      <a class="nav-link" href="/transcribe/upload">Upload File</a>
                  </li>
              </ul>
          </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="row strip">
        <img src="images/index-plane-new.jpg" class="card-img-top"/>
        <div class="strip-content card-body">
          <h2>A Proof-of-Concept Speech Recognition System Designed to help save lives</h2>
          <div class="col">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/transcribe/upload" role="button">Click here to upload an audio file for transcription</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="row about">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <h2> About the System </h2>  
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex text-center">
          <p>The aim of the project is to build a proof-of-concept system to support Air Traffic Control (ATC) messages. The system will encourage clear speech and highlight where any possible miscommunications may have occurred. 
            The system will hear what the Air Traffic Controller has said and what the pilot has said. It will then make sure the two instructions match. If the instructions do not match, then it will flag this back to the Air Traffic Controller.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <h2 class="text-center"> How it works </h2>
      <div class="col-md">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <h3>Upload file</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <i class="far fa-file-audio fa-10x"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <p>Upload an audio file to transcribe</p>
        </div>
               
      </div>
      <div class="col-md">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <h3 class="text-center">Transcribe</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <i class="far fa-comments fa-10x"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <p class="text-center">Using Google's Speech-to-Text API, the file gets transcribed to a tailored transcription</p>
        </div>
        
      </div>
      <div class="col-md">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <h3 class="text-center">Analyse</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-line fa-10x"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <p class="text-center">The text is uniquely displayed in a conversation-style layout, making it easy to understand and learn how to use</p>
        </div> 
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>




    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-JEW9xMcG8R+pH31jmWH6WWP0WintQrMb4s7ZOdauHnUtxwoG2vI5DkLtS3qm9Ekf" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
</html>
